This paper discusses recent advances in experience replay techniques for reinforcement learning, which are commonly used in the field of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper focuses on the application of these techniques in a variety of OpenAI gym environments, which suggests that it could also fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The use of DDPG and DQN methods also suggests that it could be categorized under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
